These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | soccer | water-polo | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
2. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | fishing | writing | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, fanta
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
