.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, indonesian, british
1. the indonesian is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is not to the right of the british##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | japanese | indonesian | british |

